# React + Vite

This template provides a minimal setup to get React working in Vite with HMR and some ESLint rules.

Currently, two official plugins are available:

- [@vitejs/plugin-react](https://github.com/vitejs/vite-plugin-react/blob/main/packages/plugin-react) uses [Oxc](https://oxc.rs)
- [@vitejs/plugin-react-swc](https://github.com/vitejs/vite-plugin-react/blob/main/packages/plugin-react-swc) uses [SWC](https://swc.rs/)

## React Compiler

The React Compiler is not enabled on this template because of its impact on dev & build performances. To add it, see [this documentation](https://react.dev/learn/react-compiler/installation).

## Expanding the ESLint configuration

If you are developing a production application, we recommend using TypeScript with type-aware lint rules enabled. Check out the [TS template](https://github.com/vitejs/vite/tree/main/packages/create-vite/template-react-ts) for information on how to integrate TypeScript and [`typescript-eslint`](https://typescript-eslint.io) in your project.
</file>

<file path="cliente-sistema/src/AdminDashboard.css">
.admin-dashboard-container {
  display: flex;
  min-height: 100vh;
  background-color: #fdfbf9; /* Un blanco roto ultra-limpio con calidez mínima */
  color: #3e3129; /* Texto principal oscuro y altamente legible */
  font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
}

/* SIDEBAR - MANTIENE LA IDENTIDAD CORPORATIVA OSCURA DE PANCHITA */
.admin-sidebar {
  width: 260px;
  background-color: #1a0f0a; /* Marrón profundo, elegante y ejecutivo */
  border-right: none;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  padding: 25px 15px;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  box-shadow: 4px 0 25px rgba(26, 15, 10, 0.05); /* Sombra suave hacia la derecha */
}

.sidebar-brand-box {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 35px;
}

.restaurant-logo-icon {
  font-size: 2.2rem;
  margin-bottom: 5px;
}

.sidebar-brand-box h2 {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
  color: #e5a952; /* Dorado refinado con mejor contraste */
  margin: 0;
  font-size: 1.8rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.5px;
}

.sidebar-brand-box span {
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  letter-spacing: 2px;
  color: #8c735c;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

.sidebar-menu {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 8px;
  flex-grow: 1;
}

/* MENÚ DEL SIDEBAR ACCESIBLE */
.menu-item {
  background-color: transparent;
  border: 1px solid transparent;
  color: #dcd1c4; /* Texto claro para resaltar sobre el fondo oscuro */
  text-align: left;
  padding: 12px 16px;
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  border-radius: 8px;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.25s ease;
}

.menu-item:hover, .menu-item.active {
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(229, 169, 82, 0.15) 0%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02) 100%);
  border-color: #e5a952;
  color: #fff;
  padding-left: 20px;
}

/* BOTONES DESHABILITADOS SUTILES */
.menu-item.disabled-tab {
  opacity: 0.3; /* Más transparente para que no compita con el Panel General */
  cursor: not-allowed;
  border-color: transparent;
}

.menu-item.disabled-tab:hover {
  background: transparent;
  color: #dcd1c4;
  padding-left: 16px;
}

.btn-logout-sidebar {
  background-color: transparent;
  border: 1px solid #e65100;
  color: #ff7043;
  padding: 11px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  cursor: pointer;
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  transition: all 0.2s;
  margin-top: 20px;
}

.btn-logout-sidebar:hover {
  background-color: #e65100;
  color: #fff;
}

/* ÁREA DE CONTENIDO PRINCIPAL */
.admin-main-content {
  flex-grow: 1;
  padding: 40px;
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

.view-header h1 {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
  font-size: 2.4rem;
  color: #1a0f0a; /* Título oscuro potente */
  margin: 0 0 6px 0;
}

.view-header p {
  color: #705e52; /* Subtítulo sutil y legible */
  margin: 0 0 35px 0;
  font-size: 0.95rem;
}

.highlight-text {
  color: #bc5a1a; /* Naranja/marrón quemado elegante */
  font-weight: 700;
}

/* REJILLA DE TARJETAS FLOTANTES PREMIUM */
.metrics-row-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(220px, 1fr));
  gap: 24px;
  margin-bottom: 35px;
}

.metric-card-premium {
  background-color: #ffffff; /* Tarjetas blancas limpias */
  border: 1px solid rgba(26, 15, 10, 0.04); /* Sin bordes rígidos */
  border-radius: 14px;
  padding: 24px;
  box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(26, 15, 10, 0.04); /* Efecto de suspensión en el aire */
  transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
}

.metric-card-premium:hover {
  transform: translateY(-4px); /* Pequeña animación interactiva al pasar el mouse */
  box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(26, 15, 10, 0.08);
}

.metric-header {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  font-size: 0.72rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 1px;
  color: #8c735c;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}

.metric-card-premium h2 {
  font-size: 2.3rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  color: #1a0f0a; /* Números imponentes y oscuros */
  margin: 0 0 6px 0;
  letter-spacing: -0.5px;
}

.metric-card-premium p {
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  color: #64748b; /* Gris slate para textos secundarios */
  opacity: 0.9;
  margin: 0;
}

/* ALERTAS Y TENDENCIAS */
.trend-positive { color: #2e7d32; font-weight: 600; } /* Verde éxito real */
.trend-neutral { color: #64748b; font-weight: 600; }

.badge-live {
  background-color: #fff3e0;
  color: #e65100; /* Naranja enérgico */
  padding: 2px 10px;
  border-radius: 20px;
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 0.68rem;
  border: 1px solid rgba(230, 81, 0, 0.2);
}

/* DISEÑO DE DOS COLUMNAS INFERIORES */
.dashboard-double-layout {
display: flex !important; /* Forzamos flex */
  flex-direction: row !important; /* Forzamos horizontal */
  width: 100% !important;
  gap: 25px;
  align-items: flex-start; /* Evita que las cajas se estiren innecesariamente */
}

.analytics-main-box, .live-feed-box {
  background-color: #ffffff; /* Cajas de analíticas limpias */
  border: 1px solid rgba(26, 15, 10, 0.04);
  border-radius: 14px;
  padding: 24px;
  box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(26, 15, 10, 0.04);
}

.analytics-main-box { flex: 1.8; }
.live-feed-box { flex: 1.2; }

.analytics-main-box h3, .live-feed-box h3 {
  margin: 0 0 25px 0;
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
  font-size: 1.3rem;
  color: #1a0f0a;
  font-weight: 700;
}

/* REDISEÑO DEL GRÁFICO DE BARRAS DINÁMICO */
.simulated-chart-container {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-end;
  justify-content: space-between;
  height: 220px;
  padding: 0 10px;
  border-bottom: 2px solid #f1ece7; /* Línea de base limpia */
  background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(26, 15, 10, 0.02) 1px, transparent 1px); /* Líneas de cuadrícula guía */
  background-size: 100% 40px; 
}

.chart-bar-item {
  width: 9%;
  height: var(--height);
  background-color: #f1ece7; /* Barras vacías discretas */
  border-radius: 6px 6px 0 0; /* Curvatura superior */
  position: relative;
  transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
}

.chart-bar-item:hover, .chart-bar-item.chart-bar-item--active {
  background: linear-gradient(to top, #bc5a1a 0%, #e65100 100%); /* Degradado cálido vivo */
  box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(230, 81, 0, 0.3);
}

.chart-bar-item span {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: -28px;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translateX(-50%);
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  color: #705e52;
  font-weight: 600;
}

/* MONITOREO DE ACTIVIDAD FEED (EN VIVO) */
.feed-list {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 12px;
}

.feed-item {
  padding: 14px;
  background-color: #faf8f5; /* Fondo de ítem sutil */
  border-left: 4px solid #64748b;
  border-radius: 4px 8px 8px 4px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 4px;
  transition: transform 0.2s ease;
}

.feed-item:hover {
  transform: translateX(3px);
}

.feed-time {
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  color: #8c735c;
  font-weight: 700;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

.feed-item p {
  margin: 0;
  font-size: 0.88rem;
  color: #4a3b32; /* Texto oscuro suave para los feeds */
}

/* COLORES ENERGÉTICOS PARA LOS ESTADOS EN VIVO */
.feed-item.alert-orange { border-left-color: #e65100; background-color: #fff8f5; }
.feed-item.alert-green { border-left-color: #2e7d32; background-color: #f4faf4; }
.feed-item.alert-gold { border-left-color: #bc5a1a; background-color: #fdf8f5; }
.feed-item.alert-red { border-left-color: #d32f2f; background-color: #fff5f5; }

/* ANIMACIÓN DE ENTRADA SUAVE */
.dashboard-view-fade {
  animation: viewFadeIn 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
}

@keyframes viewFadeIn {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(12px); }
  to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}

/* Opcional: Esto hace que las barras de Recharts se vean más "Panchita" */
.recharts-bar-rectangle {
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}
.recharts-bar-rectangle:hover {
  filter: brightness(1.2);
  cursor: pointer;
}
</file>

